# 
# How to set up Gmail App Password:
# 1. Enable 2-factor authentication on your Gmail account
# 2. Go to Google Account settings → Security → 2-Step Verification
# 3. Click "App passwords" and generate a password for "Mail"
# 4. Use that 16-character password as EMAIL_APP_PASSWORD
#
# How to get your Substack email:
# 1. Create a Substack publication
# 2. Go to Settings → Publishing → Email to publish
# 3. Copy the unique email address provided
